 možda ti imaš koronu

1044
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:32,560
 pa sa ćeš zaraditi svoju ženu,

1045
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,840
 zaraditi ćeš svoje dijete.

1046
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,440
 Daleko ste od

1047
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:37,400
 Zagreba, od bolnice,

1048
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,980
 najbliža bolnica je tamo.

1049
00:37:38,980 --> 00:37:39,880
 Ulici je,

1050
00:37:40,080 --> 00:37:41,640
 više od deset kilometara.

1051
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:44,140
 Ko zna kako imaju oni tamo

1052
00:37:44,140 --> 00:37:45,580
 njegu,

1053
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:47,040
 kakvi su ljudi.

1054
00:37:47,040 --> 00:37:49,060
 I sva ta pitanja su

1055
00:37:49,060 --> 00:37:49,940
 meni budila

1056
00:37:49,940 --> 00:37:51,120
 nešto što

1057
00:37:51,120 --> 00:37:54,060
 tad nisam prije

1058
00:37:54,060 --> 00:37:54,940
 ovoj nikad doživio.

1059
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,540
 ja sam inače organiziran tip

1060
00:37:57,540 --> 00:37:58,140
 i

1061
00:37:58,140 --> 00:38:00,820
 moglo bi se reći,

1062
00:38:00,820 --> 00:38:02,340
 nisam baš control freak,

1063
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:04,460
 ali volim imati sve pod kontrolom,

1064
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,300
 volim znati

1065
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:07,700
 i imati stvari na svojem mjestu.

1066
00:38:07,700 --> 00:38:09,280
 Tako da sam tu vidio

1067
00:38:09,280 --> 00:38:12,720
 lagano gubim konce u svojim rukama.

1068
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:14,280
 No, ok,

1069
00:38:14,280 --> 00:38:16,460
 pustio sam da

1070
00:38:16,460 --> 00:38:19,180
 to teče dalje.

1071
00:38:19,180 --> 00:38:20,160
 Tada još nisam znao.

1072
00:38:20,160 --> 00:38:22,460
 Pardon,

1073
00:38:22,460 --> 00:38:24,380
 tada još nisam znao kakva je to faza.

1074
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:26,360
 I

1075
00:38:26,360 --> 00:38:29,260
 da bi stvar bila još gora,

1076
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:29,940
 sad ne znam,

1077
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,200
 prvu ili drugu noć.

1078
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:33,860
 Znači to je bio kraj trećeg mjeseca.

1079
00:38:33,860 --> 00:38:36,000
 U ulici je počelo snježiti.

1080
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,520
 I

1081
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:38,460
 u roku

1082
00:38:38,460 --> 00:38:40,420
 par sati po noći

1083
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:41,880
 kada sam ja bio budan,

1084
00:38:41,880 --> 00:38:43,280
 naravno gledajući taj snijeg,

1085
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:44,380
 te pahodje koje su padale,

1086
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:46,100
 napalo je pola metra snijega.

1087
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,300
 Puh,

1088
00:38:47,300 --> 00:38:48,720
 totalni kolaps.

1089
00:38:48,720 --> 00:38:51,820
 Znači tad su još krenule misli.

1090
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:53,320
 Evo, sad će mi trebati 20 minuta

1091
00:38:53,320 --> 00:38:55,120
 da očistim auto.

1092
00:38:55,120 --> 00:38:56,980
 Ako su ceste prohodne,

1093
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:58,460
 treba će mi dva, dva i pol sata

1094
00:38:58,460 --> 00:38:59,260
 jer pada snijeg.

1095
00:38:59,560 --> 00:39:00,500
 Ako nisu prohodne,

1096
00:39:00,500 --> 00:39:02,160
 a nisu sigurno radice djetek u jutra,

1097
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:03,640
 treba će mi 3, 3,5 sata.

1098
00:39:03,640 --> 00:39:04,720
 Ko zna, ako ću uopće moć?

1099
00:39:04,720 --> 00:39:06,680
 Evo, sad ako je djete bolesno.

1100
00:39:06,680 --> 00:39:09,120
 A tim trenucima se i

1101
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:10,500
 moj sin

1102
00:39:10,500 --> 00:39:11,760
 budio

1103
00:39:11,760 --> 00:39:13,020
 češće

1104
00:39:13,020 --> 00:39:14,500
 jer je tražio hrane.

1105
00:39:14,500 --> 00:39:15,220
 Bio je gladan.

1106
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,900
 I strano, šta mu je,

1107
00:39:16,900 --> 00:39:17,640
 je li ovo dobro,

1108
00:39:17,640 --> 00:39:18,060
 je li nije?

1109
00:39:18,060 --> 00:39:20,180
 Naravno, to je meni prvo djete.

1110
00:39:20,180 --> 00:39:22,360
 Sad je to sve puno lakše.

1111
00:39:22,360 --> 00:39:26,440
 I tu su se nametnule te misli,

1112
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,640
 ti osjećaj,

1113
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,520
 ti strahovi,

1114
00:39:29,120 --> 00:39:29,720
 koje su,

1115
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:31,180
 evo, sad kako gledam,

1116
00:39:31,180 --> 00:39:32,660
 sa odmakom vremena,

1117
00:39:32,660 --> 00:39:34,220
 to je bila jedna

1118
00:39:34,220 --> 00:39:36,300
 tamna noć duha,

1119
00:39:36,300 --> 00:39:36,740
 duše,

1120
00:39:36,740 --> 00:39:37,380
 gdje je Bog,

1121
00:39:37,380 --> 00:39:39,620
 gdje je Bog te moje sjene,

1122
00:39:39,620 --> 00:39:41,860
 tu moju organiziranost,

1123
00:39:41,860 --> 00:39:43,100
 tu moju kontrolu,

1124
00:39:43,100 --> 00:39:44,940
 uspio izvući,

1125
00:39:44,940 --> 00:39:46,140
 ali svojom voljom.

1126
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:48,280
 i to je to pasivno čišćenje,

1127
00:39:48,280 --> 00:39:49,400
 ja tu nisam imao kontrole,

1128
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:50,160
 ja nisam jeo,

1129
00:39:50,160 --> 00:39:50,880
 nisam spavo,

1130
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:52,380
 nisam mogo moliti.

1131
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:53,300
 Jednostavno,

1132
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,640
 to je taj osjećaj gdje

1133
00:39:54,640 --> 00:39:56,740
 prepušteni ste Bogu

1134
00:39:56,740 --> 00:39:59,660
 i on je vaš stvoritelj,

1135
00:40:00,060 --> 00:40:00,260
 evo,

1136
00:40:00,260 --> 00:40:00,660
 Bože,

1137
00:40:00,660 --> 00:40:01,860
 Bože smilu mi se,

1138
00:40:01,860 --> 00:40:02,960
 jedino sam to mogu reći.

1139
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:08,040
 I tu dolazimo do te krive slike o Bogu,

1140
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:09,440
 gdje sam ja imao sliku

1141
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:12,820
 da će me Bog staviti u nejavu kušnju,

1142
00:40:12,820 --> 00:40:14,040
 da će Bog tražiti mene ovo,

1143
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:14,240
 evo,

1144
00:40:14,240 --> 00:40:15,900
 da ću se sad razboljati i tako dalje.

1145
00:40:15,900 --> 00:40:18,460
 To su bile te sjene u meni,

1146
00:40:18,460 --> 00:40:21,560
 no došla je iluminacija,

1147
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:22,680
 došlo je prosvjetljenje,

1148
00:40:22,680 --> 00:40:24,240
 došlo je to vječno svjetlo

1149
00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:26,920
 koje je odagnalo te sjene

1150
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:30,120
 i tada sam ja bio spreman svjetliti

1151
00:40:30,120 --> 00:40:31,040
 tim vječnim svjetlom.

1152
00:40:31,040 --> 00:40:32,600
 Znači došlo je,

1153
00:40:32,600 --> 00:40:34,180
 ajmo reći, sjedinjenje.

1154
00:40:34,840 --> 00:40:38,080
 Jedna razina sjedinjenja,

1155
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:38,980
 ne ona potpuna,

1156
00:40:38,980 --> 00:40:42,620
 ali zasigurno jedna razina

1157
00:40:42,620 --> 00:40:44,140
 je postojala ovdje.

1158
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:49,340
 Kada prođemo

1159
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:52,880
 taj proces čišćenja,

1160
00:40:52,880 --> 00:40:55,980
 neko možda još nije prošlo,

1161
00:40:55,980 --> 00:40:56,880
 neko možda je,

1162
00:40:56,880 --> 00:41:00,380
 različiti su i intenziteti,

1163
00:41:00,380 --> 00:41:02,220
 različito je vrijeme trajanja.

1164
00:41:03,060 --> 00:41:04,080
 imamo pojedine svece,

1165
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:06,300
 evo, vidimo svet Ivan Križa,

1166
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:08,100
 devet mjeseci je bio tamnici,

1167
00:41:08,100 --> 00:41:09,780
 taj je prolazio taj proces čišćenja,

1168
00:41:09,780 --> 00:41:12,440
 kasnije je napisao dijela i dijela

1169
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:14,420
 koja su obratila i potakla

1170
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:15,340
 mnoge na obraćenje.

1171
00:41:15,340 --> 00:41:17,900
 Imamo tu primjer svete Terezije

1172
00:41:17,900 --> 00:41:18,960
 od djeteta Isusa,

1173
00:41:18,960 --> 00:41:22,040
 koja je napisala

1174
00:41:22,040 --> 00:41:24,320
 u svojim dijelima

1175
00:41:24,320 --> 00:41:26,460
 da je ona imala tri faze

1176
00:41:26,460 --> 00:41:28,820
 baš te tog pasivnog čišćenja,

1177
00:41:28,820 --> 00:41:31,620
 odnosno tri puta se pasivno čistila,

1178
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:32,880
 imala je tamnu noć duše,

1179
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:35,660
 gdje je to bilo u periodima

1180
00:41:35,660 --> 00:41:36,440
 od tjedan dana,

1181
00:41:36,440 --> 00:41:37,660
 pa tri mjeseca,

1182
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:38,680
 pa godzinu dana.

1183
00:41:38,680 --> 00:41:39,640
 Tako da,

1184
00:41:39,640 --> 00:41:41,240
 gdje god vas zadesi

1185
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:43,320
 taj proces čišćenja,

1186
00:41:43,320 --> 00:41:44,100
 ne brinite se.

1187
00:41:44,100 --> 00:41:45,940
 Potražite od nekoga,

1188
00:41:45,940 --> 00:41:48,400
 jednostavno,

1189
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:50,700
 potražite nekakav razgovor

1190
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:52,520
 ili glas savjeta

1191
00:41:52,520 --> 00:41:53,920
 koji će vas dobro usmjeriti

1192
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,620
 i koji će vam znati

1193
00:41:54,620 --> 00:41:55,520
 i objasniti što je to.

1194
00:41:55,520 --> 00:41:59,860
 Znatalje,

1195
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:00,840
 nakon tog

1196
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:02,660
 procesa čišćenja,

1197
00:42:02,660 --> 00:42:03,720
 mi možemo

1198
00:42:03,720 --> 00:42:05,280
 krenuti dalje.

1199
00:42:05,280 --> 00:42:06,560
 Ono što bi

1200
00:42:06,560 --> 00:42:08,540
 naša sljedeća svetica,

1201
00:42:08,540 --> 00:42:10,600
 a to je sveta Terezija

1202
00:42:10,600 --> 00:42:11,880
 Avilska,

1203
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:13,380
 rekla,

1204
00:42:13,380 --> 00:42:15,040
 znači to je sljedeća odalja.

1205
00:42:15,040 --> 00:42:16,800
 To je, možda idemo

1206
00:42:16,800 --> 00:42:17,580
 dubliju špilju,

1207
00:42:17,580 --> 00:42:18,740
 kao što bi rekao

1208
00:42:18,740 --> 00:42:21,040
 sveti Ivan od križa.

1209
00:42:21,040 --> 00:42:22,720
 Idemo tom sjedinjenju,

1210
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:23,720
 idemo toj,

1211
00:42:23,720 --> 00:42:26,700
 tome smertom bih rekao,

1212
00:42:26,700 --> 00:42:27,560
 neokaljene točki,

1213
00:42:27,560 --> 00:42:30,900
 odnosno tom središtu

1214
00:42:30,900 --> 00:42:33,760
 gdje ćemo se mi naći sa Bogom.

1215
00:42:33,760 --> 00:42:35,880
 Sveti Ignacije

1216
00:42:35,880 --> 00:42:38,440
 lojalski

1217
00:42:38,440 --> 00:42:41,560
 kaže da to središte

1218
00:42:41,560 --> 00:42:42,600
 koje mi imamo

1219
00:42:42,600 --> 00:42:48,340
 sa gospodinom,

1220
00:42:48,340 --> 00:42:49,980
 gdje se nalazimo s njime,

1221
00:42:49,980 --> 00:42:52,220
 je kada postignemo

1222
00:42:52,220 --> 00:42:54,900
 potpuno indiferenciju.

1223
00:42:54,900 --> 00:42:56,160
 On kaže,

1224
00:42:56,160 --> 00:42:59,660
 gospodine,

1225
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:00,940
 imam li dug život

1226
00:43:00,940 --> 00:43:02,020
 ili kratak život?

1227
00:43:02,020 --> 00:43:02,840
 Svejedno mi je.

1228
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,600
 Jesam li zdrav ili bolestan?

1229
00:43:04,600 --> 00:43:05,560
 Jesam li bogat ili siromašan?

1230
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:07,940
 To je za mene indiferentno

1231
00:43:07,940 --> 00:43:09,720
 dok le god slijedim

1232
00:43:09,720 --> 00:43:10,580
 tvoju volju.

1233
00:43:10,580 --> 00:43:14,500
 Majster Ehard,

1234
00:43:14,500 --> 00:43:15,420
 isto tako jedan

1235
00:43:15,420 --> 00:43:16,800
 poznati mistik

1236
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:18,540
 i teolog

1237
00:43:18,540 --> 00:43:19,820
 iz 14. stoljeća

1238
00:43:19,820 --> 00:43:20,400
 kaže da

1239
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,700
 moramo se naći

1240
00:43:21,700 --> 00:43:22,660
 u osnovi duše

1241
00:43:22,660 --> 00:43:24,700
 sa Bogom.

1242
00:43:24,700 --> 00:43:26,480
 No,

1243
00:43:26,480 --> 00:43:27,720
 Terezija Avilska,

1244
00:43:27,720 --> 00:43:30,320
 da se vratimo na nju

1245
00:43:30,320 --> 00:43:32,700
 i da njene zamak duše,

1246
00:43:34,460 --> 00:43:34,920
 Inače,

1247
00:43:34,920 --> 00:43:37,100
 sveta Terezija Avilska

1248
00:43:37,100 --> 00:43:37,440
 je

1249
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:39,080
 meni posebna

1250
00:43:39,080 --> 00:43:39,940
 draga svetica

1251
00:43:39,940 --> 00:43:40,340
 jer

1252
00:43:40,340 --> 00:43:41,040
 na

1253
00:43:41,040 --> 00:43:43,200
 prilikom svog obračenja

1254
00:43:43,200 --> 00:43:44,580
 bio sam

1255
00:43:44,580 --> 00:43:45,940
 ustano jedan san

1256
00:43:45,940 --> 00:43:47,400
 u kojem sam se našao,

1257
00:43:47,400 --> 00:43:48,740
 zbivali su se

1258
00:43:48,740 --> 00:43:49,160
 različiti

1259
00:43:49,160 --> 00:43:51,040
 događaji,

1260
00:43:51,040 --> 00:43:51,900
 te

1261
00:43:51,900 --> 00:43:53,220
 mi je prišla jedna

1262
00:43:53,220 --> 00:43:53,640
 mlada

1263
00:43:53,640 --> 00:43:54,800
 mlada

1264
00:43:54,800 --> 00:43:56,460
 djevojka,

1265
00:43:56,460 --> 00:43:57,140
 žena

1266
00:43:57,140 --> 00:43:58,800
 i

1267
00:43:58,800 --> 00:44:00,580
 tad me je potaknula

1268
00:44:00,580 --> 00:44:00,940
 baš

1269
00:44:00,940 --> 00:44:02,180
 spantin te riječi

1270
00:44:02,180 --> 00:44:02,440
 kao

1271
00:44:02,440 --> 00:44:03,400
 dobro moliš,

1272
00:44:04,020 --> 00:44:05,080
 kao nastavi tako.

1273
00:44:05,080 --> 00:44:06,820
 Ja sad pitam

1274
00:44:06,820 --> 00:44:07,620
 pa

1275
00:44:07,620 --> 00:44:08,700
 tko si ti?

1276
00:44:08,700 --> 00:44:10,260
 Odnosno,

1277
00:44:10,260 --> 00:44:10,920
 ne, nisam pitat

1278
00:44:10,920 --> 00:44:11,480
 tko si ti,

1279
00:44:11,480 --> 00:44:12,740
 nego pitam ja

1280
00:44:12,740 --> 00:44:13,320
 pa

1281
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:16,240
 koliko ti imaš godina,

1282
00:44:16,240 --> 00:44:17,140
 koliko si već ovdje,

1283
00:44:17,140 --> 00:44:18,220
 šta se ovdje događa?

1284
00:44:18,220 --> 00:44:18,760
 Kaže ona,

1285
00:44:18,760 --> 00:44:19,080
 imam

1286
00:44:19,080 --> 00:44:20,660
 501 godinu.

1287
00:44:20,660 --> 00:44:21,540
 Pa čoveče,

1288
00:44:21,540 --> 00:44:22,100
 ja si mislim,

1289
00:44:22,100 --> 00:44:22,460
 još bio

1290
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:24,120
 obraćenik,

1291
00:44:24,120 --> 00:44:25,240
 nisam ni znao

1292
00:44:25,240 --> 00:44:26,420
 ni svece,

1293
00:44:26,420 --> 00:44:26,920
 nikako oni

1294
00:44:26,920 --> 00:44:27,560
 ne izgledaju

1295
00:44:27,560 --> 00:44:28,080
 ni ništa.

1296
00:44:31,660 --> 00:44:33,100
 gledam 501 godinu,

1297
00:44:33,100 --> 00:44:34,040
 izgleda kao da ima

1298
00:44:34,040 --> 00:44:34,460
 30,

1299
00:44:34,460 --> 00:44:36,680
 35 maksimalno.

1300
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:37,780
 Uglavnom,

1301
00:44:37,780 --> 00:44:38,600
 ona mi je pokazala

1302
00:44:38,600 --> 00:44:39,900
 još uz te riječi

1303
00:44:39,900 --> 00:44:40,380
 koje mi je putila,

1304
00:44:40,380 --> 00:44:41,620
 pokazala još neke događaje

1305
00:44:41,620 --> 00:44:44,260
 koje su,

1306
00:44:44,260 --> 00:44:45,360
 koje će se

1307
00:44:45,360 --> 00:44:46,260
 kasnije događati,

1308
00:44:46,260 --> 00:44:46,640
